---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | The Daily Drift" description="Read The Daily Drift's Privacy Policy. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you visit our website.">
  <div class="h-1.5 w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-gradient-dev-start via-violet to-highlight-pink"></div>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 prose prose-invert">
    <h1 class="font-sans font-black text-4xl text-primary uppercase">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-mute font-mono">Last Updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>
    
    <div class="space-y-6 mt-8 text-body">
      <p>Welcome to The Daily Drift. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website.</p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl text-primary">Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We may collect information about you in a variety of ways. The information we may collect via the Website includes:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Personal Data:</strong> Personally identifiable information, such as your name and email address, that you voluntarily give to us when subscribing to newsletters.</li>
        <li><strong>Derivative Data:</strong> Information our servers automatically collect when you access the Website, such as your IP address, your browser type, your operating system, your access times, and the pages you have viewed directly before and after accessing the Website.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl text-primary">Use of Your Information</h2>
      <p>Having accurate information about you permits us to provide you with a smooth, efficient, and customized experience. Specifically, we may use information collected about you via the Website to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
        <li>Deliver targeted advertising, newsletters, and other information regarding promotions and the Website to you.</li>
        <li>Compile anonymous statistical data and analysis for use internally or with third parties.</li>
        <li>Improve our Website and enhance user experience.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl text-primary">Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have questions or comments about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at contact@thedailydrift.com.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
